<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <title>New Order</title>
</head>

<body>
    <h1>You Have a New Order</h1>
    <p>Thank you for your order. We have received your request and will process it shortly.</p>
    <p>Order Details:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Order ID: <%= order._id %>
        </li>
        <li>Product: <%= order.date %>
        </li>
        <li>Quantity: <%= order.name %>
        </li>
        <li>Total Amount: <%= order.price %>
        </li>
    </ul>
    <p>We appreciate your business and will keep you updated on the order status.</p>
    <p>Thank you!</p>
</body>

</html>